               <msContents>
                  <summary>Computus, አቡሻኽር፡,</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="55v" facs="002">Fols 1r–55v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3851Hassab">We have written a
                                                  computus that we will remember in order not to
                                                  congregate with apostates...</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ንጽሕፍ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ሐሳብ፡ ዘእምፍጥረተ፡ ዓለም፡ እስከ፡ ተፍጻሜተ፡ ዓለም፡ [the text is effaced at this point] ወክፍለ፡ ሰንበታት፡ ወሱባዔሆሙ፡ ወኢዮቤላት፡ ወዑደተ፡ አንድትትዮን፡ ወክፍለ፡ ጳጕሜን፡ ወሐሳበ፡ ሰማይ፡ ወምድር፡ ወሐሳበ፡ ፀሐይ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="56r" to="77v" facs="057">Fols 56r–77v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3179Revela">Revelation of
                                                  John</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ዘዮሐንስ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ ዘቍስጥንጥንያ፡ መጥሮጶሊስ፡ አመለዎ፡ ይሰድድ፡ ራዕዩ፡ ለዮሐንስ፡ አቡ፡ ቀለምሲስ፡ ዘከመ፡ ርእዮ፡ ለኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ከመ፡ ያርእዮሙ፡ ለአግብርቲሁ፡ ዘሀለወ፡ ይኩን፡ ፍጡነ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="77v" to="79v" facs="079">Fols 77v–79v</locus><title>Book of Penance, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መጽሐፈ፡ ንስሐ፡</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Excerpt from Book of Penance, in this manuscript called <foreign xml:lang="gez">አንቀጸ፡ ንስሐ፡</foreign> or article of penance</note>
                </msItem>
